_rng().gen_range::<f64>(2.0, 100.0));\r\n}\r\n```\r\nOn my laptop the result is:\r\ntest tests::bench_rnd             ... bench:          49 ns/iter (+/- 1)\r\n\r\nBut if I run the same benchmark on JHM:\r\n\r\n```Java\r\n@Benchmark\r\npublic double testRnd() {\r\n    return ThreadLocalRandom.current().nextDouble(2, 100);\r\n}\r\n```\r\nOn my laptop the result is:\r\nBenchmark     Mode  Cnt  Score   Error  Units\r\nMain.testRnd  avgt   20  9,018 \u00b1 0,094  ns/op\r\n\r\nSo the difference is 5.44 times looks like performance bug.\r\n\r\n## Meta\r\nRust:\r\n\r\nrbose\r\nrustc 1.20.0-nightly (c9bb93576 2017-06-24)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: c9bb93576d4484edd1b3c40eb2aea0dfa0788851\r\ncommit-date: 2017-06-24\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nrelease: 1.20.0-nightly\r\nLLVM version: 4.0\r\n\r\nJava:\r\nOpenJDK 1.8.131", "closed_by": {"login": "SharplEr", "id": 2966206, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5NjYyMDY=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2966206?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr", "html_url": "https://github.com/SharplEr", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SharplEr/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43120/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "ti